reviewText: I have this exercise video when i was pregnant my 12 year daughter , i was in the  best shape of my life , best exercise video ever  thanks Kathy.

This is a great work out for those who are pregnant.  I love this work out helps to keep you fit and tone.  The after pregnancy work out is great as well to get you back in tone after the baby.  I think this work out helped me a great deal and made me that much better in shape when labor came.  I highly recommend this work out.
